title: Engaged
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Wonbo, are you going to propose on the cruise?! 
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
(Fake nervous laughter) HAHAHAHA 
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Why are you laughing?
Oh my god you are... that is so cliche.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>

Also, if you want to be completely surprised, stop asking!!
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Then when are you going to??
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>

<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
